    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Kingdom of Cards and Tiles</strong> 是一款结合经典桌游的游戏，如 <i><strong>Carcassonne</strong></i> 和 <i><strong>Clank! A Deck-Building Adventure</strong></i>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263850/extras/07718300b0af02e17a6e28b7768fc5fc.avif?t=1743792503\" width=800 height=272 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >结合卡牌和神器，创造多样化的协同效果和策略组合。购买新卡牌来丰富您的牌组，并在故事中不断前进，同时发现隐藏的任务、卡牌奖励和神器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263850/extras/3a46131e3529ffd52cb07cba9e0b181d.avif?t=1743792503\" width=521 height=102 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >经典的桌游和卡组构建体验。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >独特故事的战役模式。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可解锁的卡牌和神器。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul>",
